snippet.title: Death Taxi 3000 - new career gameplay [DOSBox-Staging 0.75.1]
snippet.description: Just doing some test capture of the upcoming version 1.3.3 on the latest DOSBox-Staging. I was looking for alternatives for DOSBox 0.73 on Linux because of some bugs with the old SDL 1.2 input handling.
